{"tid":971442,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(垃圾即係垃圾) 比亞迪供港電動的士 最後一輛已被送到劏車場","createTime":"2019-01-06T15:34:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-06T15:34:18.000Z","uid":2104,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"10dc092eacccdbf43b1103447e4f5a8f0dd1e83f","tid":971442,"uid":2104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T15:34:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i2UykNG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi2UykNG.png&h=50353947&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2013 年政府推出先導計劃，引進了 4 部比亞迪電動的士，希望測試在香港使用電動的士的可行性。事隔約 5 年，最後一部電動的士早前已經被送往劏車便當作廢鐵。擁有該部電動的士的黃永忠指責政府欠缺支援，未有對維修和更換電池作出補貼。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SwoOT6L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSwoOT6L.png&h=385e7ec4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黃永忠又指政府要求他支付 30 萬稅款，方可以將以超過 30 萬購入的電動的士改為私家車使用。他表示 2013 年推行的先導計劃失敗收場，比亞迪的電動的士續航距離不足，電力系統亦出現問題，但的士在保養期過後則沒有支援，令他迫於無奈放棄。他又指自己一直駕駛石油氣的士，電動的士的成本太高。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好快到假豐田小巴同城巴啲新青年巴士<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.thestandard.com.hk/section-news.php?id=203711&amp;story_id=50027995\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandard.com.hk%2Fsection-news.php%3Fid%3D203711%26story_id%3D50027995&d=1Ez4rSi7KZ%2BOFoN8eJ2EiY9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=c638c291\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.thestandard.com.hk/section-news.php?id=203711&amp;story_id=50027995</a>"}]}